Summary: Nighttime Rods or New Entity Video
divs: Sighting DetailsI shoot some Video on June 29th at 9:30PM of 2 Flying Rods and with the movement of the second on the footage I may be the first to have filmed them. There are 2 Rods in the Video the first comes up from the ground and bends around the phone line above. The second is the best it comes in from a horiziontal pattern then in front of the camera stops and the backside of it swings into a different position then takes the lead in that other direction, amazing! I was filming trying to capture lightning from a storm to the west of my home and this is what I caught. The camera was a Sony Handycam HCR-DVD105 using manual focus and Super Nightshot Plus mounted on a tripod. I just bought the camera that day (not kidding)and This was my first Video and I was lucky enough to capture this footage. The Video has to be slowed down to see the backend swing into that next position. Hopefully I have discovered maybe a new entity or a Real Rod and this clearly shows its not an insect. I saved the original Mini DVD in case someone wants to examine it.
